
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-nir-ipsecme-p2p-00.txt'>
    <title>"Creating Large Scale Mesh VPNs Problem Statement", Yoav Nir, John Veizades, Chris Ulliott, Jorge Mendoza</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-nir-ipsecme-p2p-00.txt</link>
    <description>This document presents the problem of configuring a large number of IKE/IPsec systems in such a way that any two of them can use IPsec to protect the traffic between them.  Manual configuration of all possible tunnels is too cumbersome in such cases, so an automated method is needed.</description>
    <dc:date>2011-10-12T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
